00:21:54.470 --> 00:21:56.620 align:middle line:84%
The global economy,
that's collapsing

00:21:56.620 --> 00:21:58.680 align:middle line:84%
as we have this
conversation right now,

00:21:58.680 --> 00:22:01.690 align:middle line:84%
it is based on survival
of the strongest.

00:22:01.690 --> 00:22:05.470 align:middle line:84%
And the way we solve many of our
problems in the 20th century,

00:22:05.470 --> 00:22:08.530 align:middle line:84%
a time that historians tell
us was the bloodiest century

00:22:08.530 --> 00:22:11.890 align:middle line:84%
in all of recorded human
history, is based on this idea

00:22:11.890 --> 00:22:15.490 align:middle line:84%
that there's a pie,
one pie, and that we've

00:22:15.490 --> 00:22:19.690 align:middle line:84%
got to fight for the
biggest slice of that pie.

00:22:19.690 --> 00:22:23.260 align:middle line:84%
The problem with all of this is
the new discoveries very, very

00:22:23.260 --> 00:22:27.730 align:middle line:84%
clearly are telling us that
while competition does happen

00:22:27.730 --> 00:22:30.880 align:middle line:84%
in some circumstances,
and we've all seen it,

00:22:30.880 --> 00:22:34.240 align:middle line:84%
