see in nature is not

00:23:31.570 --> 00:23:33.250 align:middle line:90%
every animal out for itself.

00:23:33.250 --> 00:23:37.900 align:middle line:84%
We see cooperation, he said,
is an incredibly successful

00:23:37.900 --> 00:23:39.160 align:middle line:90%
strategy for survival.

00:23:39.160 --> 00:23:42.640 align:middle line:84%
When cooperation breaks down,
the results can be disastrous.

