false assumptions of science.

00:45:04.200 --> 00:45:07.850 align:middle line:84%
Little shifts that we
make in our personal lives

00:45:07.850 --> 00:45:11.000 align:middle line:84%
translate into huge
changes in a relatively

00:45:11.000 --> 00:45:12.570 align:middle line:90%
