no longer exists and are
working to get back to that,

00:46:56.286 --> 00:46:57.660 align:middle line:84%
I think they're
the ones that are

00:46:57.660 --> 00:47:01.260 align:middle line:84%
having the greatest struggle,
the greatest suffering.

00:47:01.260 --> 00:47:03.360 align:middle line:84%
So the world of
the past is gone.

00:47:03.360 --> 00:47:06.450 align:middle line:84%
We cannot go back to it,
because it no longer exists.

00:47:06.450 --> 00:47:08.170 align:middle line:84%
We're moving
forward with change.

00:47:08.170 --> 00:47:08.970 align:middle line:90%
That is a fact.

00:47:08.970 --> 00:47:09.870 align:middle line:90%
Are we going to stop it?

00:47:09.870 --> 00:47:10.670 align:middle line:90%
Probably not.

00:47:10.670 --> 00:47:11.730 align:middle line:90%
That's a fact.

00:47:11.730 --> 00:47:13.500 align:middle line:90%
Can we direct the change?

00:47:13.500 --> 00:47:14.490 align:middle line:90%
I believe we can.

00:47:14.490 --> 00:47:17.040 align:middle line:84%
Can we soften the
impact of how that

00:47:17.040 --> 00:47:20.250 align:middle line:84%
change lands in our personal
and our collective lives?

00:47:20.250 --> 00:47:22.289 align:middle line:84%
The evidence suggests
that we can, strongly.

00:47:22.289 --> 00:47:24.330 align:middle line:84%
So let me just say this
briefly, and I don't know

00:47:24.330 --> 00:47:26.414 align:middle line:84%
how we're doing on
our time here, but--

00:47:26.414 --> 00:47:27.330 align:middle line:90%
>> We've got about 10.

00:47:27.330 --> 00:47:29.500 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:47:29.500 --> 00:47:32.800 align:middle line:90%
Let me share a story.

00:47:32.800 --> 00:47:37.770 align:middle line:84%
I was in Australia over
9/11 and couldn't get back

00:47:37.770 --> 00:47:39.000 align:middle line:90%
in my own country.

00:47:39.000 --> 00:47:40.440 align:middle line:90%
Planes weren't flying.

00:47:40.440 --> 00:47:43.340 align:middle line:84%
And when they did, I came back,
and just a few days later, I

00:47:43.340 --> 00:47:48.770 align:middle line:84%
was actually in Paris,
France, right after 9/11.

00:47:48.770 --> 00:47:51.140 align:middle line:84%
And I was with an
audience of 3,500 people.

00:47:51.140 --> 00:47:53.690 align:middle line:84%
And there was one man in the
audience, a Frenchman, who

00:47:53.690 --> 00:47:55.170 align:middle line:90%
was very angry about something.

00:47:55.170 --> 00:47:56.711 align:middle line:84%
Security came in,
and they were going

00:47:56.711 --> 00:47:58.860 align:middle line:90%
to kick him out of the venue.

00:47:58.860 --> 00:48:00.450 align:middle line:84%
I believe there
are no accidents.

00:48:00.450 --> 00:48:01.855 align:middle line:90%
So I said, don't kick him out.

00:48:01.855 --> 00:48:03.480 align:middle line:84%
I said, if you want
to ask him to stand

00:48:03.480 --> 00:48:05.900 align:middle line:90%
in the hall for three minutes.

00:48:05.900 --> 00:48:08.340 align:middle line:84%
Ask him just to
wait in the hall.

00:48:08.340 --> 00:48:10.880 align:middle line:84%
And while he was gone
in those three minutes,

00:48:10.880 --> 00:48:16.280 align:middle line:84%
the 3,499 people now left
in the 3,500-seat audience,

00:48:16.280 --> 00:48:21.060 align:middle line:84%
we went through an exercise
creating what's called

00:48:21.060 --> 00:48:23.650 align:middle line:84%
coherence between the
heart and the brain.

00:48:23.650 --> 00:48:26.640 align:middle line:84%
It is scientifically
proven to be

00:48:26.640 --> 00:48:28.680 align:middle line:84%
the core of some of
our most spiritual

00:48:28.680 --> 00:48:30.810 align:middle line:90%
and ancient traditions.

00:48:30.810 --> 00:48:33.780 align:middle line:84%
It's about setting up
communication between the heart

00:48:33.780 --> 00:48:37.500 align:middle line:84%
and the brain of a very
low frequency, 0.10 hertz.

00:48:37.500 --> 00:48:40.740 align:middle line:90%
Heart-brain coherence.

00:48:40.740 --> 00:48:41.710 align:middle line:90%
It's very easy to do.

00:48:41.710 --> 00:48:42.190 align:middle line:90%
It's based on--

00:48:42.190 --> 00:48:43.356 align:middle line:90%
>> Heart Math works on this.

00:48:43.356 --> 00:48:45.060 align:middle line:84%
>> It's what we
do in our hearts,

00:48:45.060 --> 00:48:47.520 align:middle line:84%
and it's based on studies,
now scientifically proven,

00:48:47.520 --> 00:48:50.070 align:middle line:84%
through the Institute
of Heart Math.

00:48:50.070 --> 00:48:51.245 align:middle line:90%
I think Howard Martin--

00:48:51.245 --> 00:48:53.050 align:middle line:84%
I believe you've
interviewed Howard Martin.

00:48:53.050 --> 00:48:54.810 align:middle line:84%
>> No, we have not
gotten together yet.

00:48:54.810 --> 00:48:57.000 align:middle line:84%
>> OK, he's a dear brother,
colleague, and friend.

00:48:57.000 --> 00:48:57.180 align:middle line:90%
>> Please put in a word.

00:48:57.180 --> 00:48:59.490 align:middle line:84%
>> And the person that can make
that happen is in the room with

00:48:59.490 --> 00:48:59.960 align:middle line:90%
us now.

00:48:59.960 --> 00:49:00.413 align:middle line:90%
>> Is you.

00:49:00.413 --> 00:49:01.560 align:middle line:90%
Would you please?

00:49:01.560 --> 00:49:02.500 align:middle line:90%
>> We will.

00:49:02.500 --> 00:49:02.930 align:middle line:90%
>> I've done Heart--

00:49:02.930 --> 00:49:03.890 align:middle line:90%
I have done that.

00:49:03.890 --> 00:49:05.765 align:middle line:84%
>> He's here this week,
and I'd like for you,

00:49:05.765 --> 00:49:06.900 align:middle line:90%
if you can talk to him.

00:49:06.900 --> 00:49:08.490 align:middle line:90%
Here's the key.

00:49:08.490 --> 00:49:13.760 align:middle line:84%
Coherence is easy to achieve,
and it is measurable.

00:49:13.760 --> 00:49:17.130 align:middle line:84%
And when we establish
heart-brain coherence

00:49:17.130 --> 00:49:19.830 align:middle line:84%
based upon experiences
that are taught in some

00:49:19.830 --> 00:49:24.720 align:middle line:84%
are most cherished and ancient
spiritual traditions, what

00:49:24.720 --> 00:49:26.250 align:middle line:90%
we do is we set up a field.

00:49:26.250 --> 00:49:29.940 align:middle line:84%
We couple the magnetic
field of the human heart

00:49:29.940 --> 00:49:32.340 align:middle line:84%
with the magnetic
field of the Earth that

00:49:32.340 --> 00:49:33.750 align:middle line:90%
connects and sustains all life.

00:49:33.750 --> 00:49:37.420 align:middle line:84%
So it is a marriage
of us with this field.

00:49:37.420 --> 00:49:42.690 align:middle line:84%
So in this room, ballroom in
Paris, I invited the group

00:49:42.690 --> 00:49:45.030 align:middle line:84%
and shared with them
very simple instructions

00:49:45.030 --> 00:49:47.252 align:middle line:84%
to set up a coherent
field in the room.

00:49:47.252 --> 00:49:48.210 align:middle line:90%
And you can measure it.

00:49:48.210 --> 00:49:50.180 align:middle line:90%
We know it was actually there.

00:49:50.180 --> 00:49:52.160 align:middle line:84%
Then, we invited the
Frenchman to come back in,

00:49:52.160 --> 00:49:53.130 align:middle line:90%
gave him a microphone.

00:49:53.130 --> 00:49:56.130 align:middle line:84%
Through the translator,
because my French is terrible,

00:49:56.130 --> 00:49:59.035 align:middle line:84%
I asked him, I said, tell
us what your experience is.

00:49:59.035 --> 00:49:59.910 align:middle line:90%
What are you feeling?

00:49:59.910 --> 00:50:02.580 align:middle line:84%
And he had the strangest
look on his face.

00:50:02.580 --> 00:50:04.260 align:middle line:84%
And he said, through
the translator,

00:50:04.260 --> 00:50:06.490 align:middle line:84%
he said, in my mind,
I know why I'm angry.

00:50:06.490 --> 00:50:08.430 align:middle line:84%
He says, but I can't
feel the anger.

00:50:08.430 --> 00:50:11.180 align:middle line:90%
He couldn't access the emotion.

00:50:11.180 --> 00:50:15.180 align:middle line:84%
And I'm not surprised,
because in a coherent field,

00:50:15.180 --> 00:50:18.690 align:middle line:84%
the emotion of anger and
hate and jealousy and rage

00:50:18.690 --> 00:50:21.690 align:middle line:84%
that fuels competition,
that is no longer present.

00:50:21.690 --> 00:50:23.954 align:middle line:84%
You can think about it,
but you can't feel it.

00:50:23.954 --> 00:50:26.370 align:middle line:84%
The reason I'm sharing that
story is because what happened

00:50:26.370 --> 00:50:28.080 align:middle line:84%
in that room with
that man can happen

00:50:28.080 --> 00:50:30.300 align:middle line:90%
on a planet between nations.

00:50:30.300 --> 00:50:34.200 align:middle line:84%
It's really hard for
a leader of any nation

00:50:34.200 --> 00:50:37.590 align:middle line:84%
to declare war on their neighbor
when you're not feeling it.

00:50:37.590 --> 00:50:40.170 align:middle line:84%
You know, you can talk to
your Joint Chiefs of Staff,

00:50:40.170 --> 00:50:43.590 align:middle line:84%
and you can say, hey, guys,
I'm just not feeling it.

00:50:43.590 --> 00:50:49.050 align:middle line:84%
It's really hard to declare
a violent competition

00:50:49.050 --> 00:50:50.550 align:middle line:90%
of any kind.

00:50:50.550 --> 00:50:54.090 align:middle line:84%
And this, I think, is one of
the greatest hopes in our world

00:50:54.090 --> 00:50:55.820 align:middle line:84%
today, because there
is no them and us

00:50:55.820 --> 00:50:56.750 align:middle line:90%
when it comes to this field.

00:50:56.750 --> 00:50:57.550 align:middle line:90%
There's a we.

00:50:57.550 --> 00:51:01.470 align:middle line:84%
Every CEO of every corporation,
every leader of every nation,

00:51:01.470 --> 00:51:03.860 align:middle line:84%
every blade of grass, every
hamster, every goldfish,

00:51:03.860 --> 00:51:07.790 align:middle line:84%
every dog, every cat is
linked to this field.

00:51:07.790 --> 00:51:10.520 align:middle line:84%
The question is, what
do we-- because we're

00:51:10.520 --> 00:51:13.310 align:middle line:84%
linked to it every day,
what do we feed the field?

00:51:13.310 --> 00:51:15.829 align:middle line:84%
What do we have to nurture
and nourish this field with?

00:51:15.829 --> 00:51:17.870 align:middle line:84%
Now, this is where it gets
really tricky, Regina.

00:51:17.870 --> 00:51:20.250 align:middle line:90%
I'm being careful about this.

00:51:20.250 --> 00:51:22.940 align:middle line:84%
People ask me if I was
supporting the Occupy Movement

00:51:22.940 --> 00:51:25.580 align:middle line:90%
as it existed in the early days.

00:51:25.580 --> 00:51:28.610 align:middle line:84%
And I said to them,
very honestly,

00:51:28.610 --> 00:51:30.410 align:middle line:90%
the system is definitely broken.

00:51:30.410 --> 00:51:33.790 align:middle line:90%
We definitely need a new system.

00:51:33.790 --> 00:51:37.610 align:middle line:84%
I am all about, and will always
work for, positive change,

00:51:37.610 --> 00:51:41.390 align:middle line:84%
but you will never see me
fight against or protest

00:51:41.390 --> 00:51:44.990 align:middle line:84%
against something
for this very reason.

00:51:44.990 --> 00:51:46.880 align:middle line:90%
There's a field out there.

00:51:46.880 --> 00:51:49.340 align:middle line:84%
The field doesn't
know the specifics.

00:51:49.340 --> 00:51:51.650 align:middle line:84%
It gets the general
patterns of energy.

00:51:51.650 --> 00:51:54.470 align:middle line:84%
When we're protesting against
something, what we're doing

00:51:54.470 --> 00:52:00.620 align:middle line:84%
is causing a very incohesive
disruption in this field that

00:52:00.620 --> 00:52:03.020 align:middle line:90%
agitates and upsets people.

00:52:03.020 --> 00:52:06.140 align:middle line:84%
So I will work to create
a field of coherence

00:52:06.140 --> 00:52:07.910 align:middle line:90%
toward positive change.

00:52:07.910 --> 00:52:10.010 align:middle line:84%
I would never tear
down something

00:52:10.010 --> 00:52:12.830 align:middle line:84%
that is already existing,
because from my perspective,

00:52:12.830 --> 00:52:15.170 align:middle line:84%
my understanding and what
I know now to be true,

00:52:15.170 --> 00:52:17.850 align:middle line:84%
it actually defeats
the very purpose

00:52:17.850 --> 00:52:20.210 align:middle line:84%
and actually supports
the conditions

00:52:20.210 --> 00:52:22.742 align:middle line:90%
that we would like to change.

00:52:22.742 --> 00:52:24.450 align:middle line:84%
So I don't know if I
said that OK or not.

00:52:24.450 --> 00:52:28.670 align:middle line:84%
>> No, no, that was, to
me, that was perfectly put.

00:52:28.670 --> 00:52:30.050 align:middle line:90%
And that is at the crux of it.

00:52:30.050 --> 00:52:33.330 align:middle line:84%
Because we're all now having
to take in so much information,

00:52:33.330 --> 00:52:35.270 align:middle line:84%
evaluate, look at
what doesn't work.

00:52:35.270 --> 00:52:38.055 align:middle line:84%
And naturally, it attracts
anger in a lot of people--

00:52:38.055 --> 00:52:38.930 align:middle line:90%
>> I understand that.

00:52:38.930 --> 00:52:40.596 align:middle line:84%
>> --when you find
you've been deceived.

00:52:40.596 --> 00:52:41.900 align:middle line:90%
>> I understand that.

00:52:41.900 --> 00:52:44.570 align:middle line:84%
>> Your resources have
been misallocated.

00:52:44.570 --> 00:52:45.800 align:middle line:90%
People get upset about it.

00:52:45.800 --> 00:52:47.660 align:middle line:90%
But still, the temptation--

00:52:47.660 --> 00:52:50.570 align:middle line:84%
I know the temptation is there
to want to lash out and indulge

00:52:50.570 --> 00:52:51.437 align:middle line:90%
in these feelings.

00:52:51.437 --> 00:52:52.520 align:middle line:90%
It's not helping anything.

00:52:52.520 --> 00:52:55.310 align:middle line:84%
>> Now that we know the
relationships when we create

00:52:55.310 --> 00:52:57.150 align:middle line:90%
