00:53:10.740 --> 00:53:13.430 align:middle line:84%
And we all feel that
in one way or another.

00:53:13.430 --> 00:53:15.380 align:middle line:84%
Coherence can offset
that a little bit

00:53:15.380 --> 00:53:18.020 align:middle line:84%
and maybe help even out
some of those rough edges.

00:53:18.020 --> 00:53:21.860 align:middle line:84%
When people are protesting
against something

00:53:21.860 --> 00:53:24.020 align:middle line:84%
that they don't
believe in, the field

00:53:24.020 --> 00:53:29.210 align:middle line:84%
doesn't make a distinction
between their beliefs and--

00:53:29.210 --> 00:53:32.570 align:middle line:84%
all the field knows is there is
an agitation from their protest

00:53:32.570 --> 00:53:34.440 align:middle line:84%
