out into the field.

00:53:34.440 --> 00:53:39.110 align:middle line:84%
So this is where if we're really
conscious of our relationship

00:53:39.110 --> 00:53:43.550 align:middle line:84%
to the Earth and to one
another and if we really

00:53:43.550 --> 00:53:46.550 align:middle line:84%
understand these principles,
this is what's different now.

00:53:46.550 --> 00:53:51.050 align:middle line:84%
Relatively few people can
anchor a very powerful field

00:53:51.050 --> 00:53:54.320 align:middle line:84%
of coherence that smooths out
some of those rough edges.

00:53:54.320 --> 00:53:57.230 align:middle line:84%
And I think when it
comes down to making

00:53:57.230 --> 00:53:59.480 align:middle line:84%
those choices, somebody
sitting in a room

00:53:59.480 --> 00:54:01.150 align:middle line:84%
halfway around the
world saying, are we

00:54:01.150 --> 00:54:04.970 align:middle line:90%
