00:54:04.970 --> 00:54:08.510 align:middle line:84%
It's really hard
to go to war when,

00:54:08.510 --> 00:54:10.850 align:middle line:84%
in the field of
coherence, you're

00:54:10.850 --> 00:54:18.584 align:middle line:84%
feeling the desire for
peace and cooperation.

00:54:18.584 --> 00:54:20.250 align:middle line:84%
And this is what the
studies have shown.

00:54:20.250 --> 00:54:22.020 align:middle line:84%
In the presence of
coherence, we're

00:54:22.020 --> 00:54:26.460 align:middle line:84%
much less violent, much
more willing to cooperate,

00:54:26.460 --> 00:54:28.110 align:middle line:90%
much less warlike.

00:54:28.110 --> 00:54:29.670 align:middle line:90%
Plus, it's healthy for us.

00:54:29.670 --> 00:54:30.490 align:middle line:90%
It's good for us.

00:54:30.490 --> 00:54:31.710 align:middle line:90%
>> It's a personal choice.

00:54:31.710 --> 00:54:32.510 align:middle line:90%
>> It is.

00:54:32.510 --> 00:54:33.960 align:middle line:90%
Coherence, individual coherence.

00:54:33.960 --> 00:54:35.520 align:middle line:84%
It strengthens
our immune system.

00:54:35.520 --> 00:54:37.170 align:middle line:84%
Kicks those anti-aging
hormones in--

00:54:37.170 --> 00:54:38.340 align:middle line:90%
